data.message: How do I get my friends day video on my fb page?  This is so cool....seeing it on others, but not mine.

replies.message: Hi Diana. If you have enough content for us to create a video, it will appear in your News Feed. You can also visit http://on.fb.me/1UOjwKP to see your video when it's ready. Thanks for stopping by! -Rey
